title: tellmMore.... english for kids
description:
kids!!! lets start to learn english

 TELL ME MORE utilizes the same methods used by many primary school teachers. By utilizing English exercises that are interactive and fun, your child will enjoy learning English quickly and effectively thanks to the use of voice recognition technology. This solution incorporates many fun activities suitable for children including cartoons, karaoke songs, Memory games, and much more.
 This solution contains 3 Software CD/DVDs.
